io.sphere.sdk.products.queries

Interface ProductProjectionQuery

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ExpansionPathContainer<ProductProjection>, MetaModelQueryDsl<ProductProjection,ProductProjectionQuery,ProductProjectionQueryModel,ProductProjectionExpansionModel<ProductProjection>>, MetaModelReferenceExpansionDsl<ProductProjection,ProductProjectionQuery,ProductProjectionExpansionModel<ProductProjection>>, Query<ProductProjection>, QueryDsl<ProductProjection,ProductProjectionQuery>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<ProductProjection,ProductProjectionQuery>, ReferenceExpansionSupport<ProductProjection>, ResourceQuery<ProductProjection>, SphereRequest<PagedQueryResult<ProductProjection>>

    public interface ProductProjectionQuery
extends MetaModelQueryDsl<ProductProjection,ProductProjectionQuery,ProductProjectionQueryModel,ProductProjectionExpansionModel<ProductProjection>>
    Provides a QueryDsl for product projections to formulate predicates, search expressions and reference expansion path expressions.

    For further information how to use the query API to consult the Query API documentation.
